---
layout: base.njk
title: Types
permalink: /types/
---
<h1 class="page-title">Browse by type</h1>
<p class="page-intro">The same notebook, sliced by format. Types are loose, not a fixed list.</p>

<div class="chip-list" style="gap: var(--space-sm); margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
  {%- for type in collections.entryTypes %}
    {%- set count = 0 %}
    {%- for entry in collections.entries %}
      {%- if entry.data.type == type %}{% set count = count + 1 %}{% endif %}
    {%- endfor %}
  <a class="chip" href="{{ ('/types/' + (type | slugify) + '/') | url }}">{{ type }} <span style="opacity:.6">({{ count }})</span></a>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>
